OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774793495
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'loving' mother,
OL,4,Csister and aunt murdered in her home
OL,6,FA 49-year-old man has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of the murder of his "kind,
OL,8,Fintelligent" girlfriend, who he
OL,9,Fsuffocated by wrapping tape around her
OL,10,Fface.
OL,12,FNorbert Maiksner was convicted
OL,13,Ffollowing a trial at Portsmouth Crown
OL,14,FCourt.
OL,16,FHe killed 45-year-old Frances
OL,17,FObiefuleh at their home in Havant,
OL,18,FHampshire.
OL,20,FHe was also charged with child neglect.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
