PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774793495
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'loving' mother,
OL,4,Csister and aunt murdered in her home
OL,6,FPaying tribute to Ms Obiefuleh, her
OL,7,Ffamily said: "Frances was kind,
OL,8,Fintelligent, and resourceful - a
OL,9,Fcaring and deeply loving mother,
OL,10,Fsister, aunt, and friend to many.
OL,12,F"She was a devoted mother and
OL,13,Fbeautiful in every sense of the word.
OL,15,F"Someone we love has been cruelly
OL,16,Ftaken from us, and it has changed our
OL,17,Flives forever.
OL,19,F"We have lost a truly beautiful soul.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774793495
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'loving' mother,
OL,4,Csister and aunt murdered in her home
OL,6,F"Her bright light has been cruelly
OL,7,Fdimmed, and we are left shaken,
OL,8,Fheartbroken, and still trying to
OL,9,Fprocess the grief and shock of losing
OL,10,FFrances."
OL,12,FPaul Cavin KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,13,Fcourt that the defendant was found by
OL,14,Fa Highways Officer walking along the
OL,15,Fhard shoulder of the M40 motorway near
OL,16,FHigh Wycombe, Buckinghamshire, on the
OL,17,Fmorning of April 17 2025.
OL,19,FHe told the officer that they should
OL,20,Fcall the police because he had killed
OL,21,Fhis girlfriend.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774793495
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'loving' mother,
OL,4,Csister and aunt murdered in her home
OL,6,FMr Cavin said that a post-mortem
OL,7,Fexamination revealed she died of
OL,8,Fsmothering with injuries caused by
OL,9,Fcompression of the neck and chest.
OL,11,FHe said the defendant also had
OL,12,Fscratches to his chest and back, and
OL,13,Fadded: "The likely and frankly
OL,14,Fterrible conclusion is that they were
OL,15,Finflicted by Frances with her fingers
OL,16,Fand fingernails during the attack by
OL,17,Fthe defendant in her last moments as
OL,18,Fshe struggled to stay alive."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
