OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774793495
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'loving' mother,
OL,4,Csister and aunt murdered in her home
OL,6,FA Hampshire Constabulary spokesman
OL,7,Fsaid that Maiksner had not attended
OL,8,Fthe trial and it had gone ahead in his
OL,9,Fabsence.
OL,11,FThe force spokesman said: "During his
OL,12,Ftrial the court heard that Maiksner
OL,13,Fhad told officers that he had killed
OL,14,FFrances and stated that it was all a
OL,15,Fdream and that he wanted to wake up."
OL,17,FMaiksner will be sentenced on March 30.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
